OL,3,CFormer Co-op bank boss ordered to pay
OL,4,C#184,000 or face jail
OL,6,FFormer Co-operative Bank chairman has
OL,7,Fbeen ordered by a judge to pay back
OL,8,F#184,000 he stole from a "vulnerable"
OL,9,Felderly woman with dementia.
OL,11,FPaul Flowers, 75, betrayed his friend
OL,12,Fof many years, Margaret Jarvis, before
OL,13,Fusing her money on drugs, holidays,
OL,14,Fand gifts for himself after she
OL,15,Fdeveloped progressive dementia.
