OL,6,FA former Labour councillor in Rochdale
OL,7,Fand Bradford, and church minister,
OL,8,FFlowers had been made power of
OL,9,Fattorney and executor of the will of
OL,10,FMargaret, a retired teacher who never
OL,11,Fmarried.
OL,13,FDubbed the "Crystal Methodist," he
OL,14,Fpleaded guilty to multiple counts of
OL,15,Ffraud in July 2024 at Manchester Crown
OL,16,FCourt and was jailed for three years.
