OL,3,CFormer Co-op bank boss ordered to pay
OL,4,C#184,000 or face jail
OL,6,FHe will have two and a half years
OL,7,Fadded to that prison sentence if he
OL,8,Fdoes not pay the full amount ordered
OL,9,Fon Wednesday 24 September within the
OL,10,Fnext three months, after the Crown
OL,11,FProsecution Service (CPS) secured a
OL,12,Fconfiscation order from a judge for
OL,13,F#184,862.
OL,15,FCharles Clayton, specialist prosecutor
OL,16,Fof CPS Proceeds of Crime Division,
OL,17,Fsaid: "Paul Flowers abused the trust
OL,18,Fhis friend placed in him, preying on
OL,19,Fher vulnerability.
