OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F399A1758826433
OL,3,CFormer Co-op bank boss ordered to pay
OL,4,C#184,000 or face jail
OL,6,F"Today CPS Proceeds of Crime Division
OL,7,Fensured that Flowers cannot continue
OL,8,Fto benefit from his ill-gotten gains
OL,9,Fand his victim's final wishes for her
OL,10,Festate will finally be fulfilled."
OL,12,FHe continued taking her cash after her
OL,13,Fdeath, aged 82, in 2016 in a care home
OL,14,Fnear Amersham, in Buckinghamshire.
OL,16,FAn analysis of transactions by Flowers
OL,17,Fshowed he had used Margaret's money to
OL,18,Fbuy theatre tickets, fine wines,
OL,19,Fcruise holidays, stays at the Park
OL,20,FHotel in Knightsbridge and tickets for
OL,21,Fthe West End show Jersey Boys.
