OL,6,FFlowers was dubbed the "Crystal
OL,7,FMethodist" after footage was published
OL,8,Fof the former church minister handing
OL,9,Fover #300 in cash for crystal meth and
OL,10,Fother drugs in Leeds in November 2013.
OL,12,FHe pleaded guilty at Leeds
OL,13,FMagistrates' Court to possessing
OL,14,Fcocaine, crystal meth, and ketamine,
OL,15,Fand was fined #400.
